Outside, there are demons, magical beasts, and

Oh my! It's hard to know where to look!

Outside, there are demons, magical beasts, and
bandits... There's nowhere safe.

Oh, you've come at a good time, magical girl.
Actually, it seems like I dropped an important
charm that I received from my sister in the cave
of the barrier.

The barrier cave is located north of the town, and
I'm certain there are barrier pillars installed
there.

Yeah, that cave is also a shortcut that leads to
the northern plains, so I used it quite often...

The charm, huh... Should we try looking for it
just in case? Someone might have already taken it
though.

Since it's a charm that my sister made for me with
great effort, I really want to find it if
possible.

Alright, I got it. If we find it, I'll make sure
to deliver it to you. But well, it might be better
not to get your hopes up too much.
Thank you! I'm Santou. Nice to meet you. And you?

Sorry, I'm a bit busy right now, so let's talk
later.
ここでアイテムゲット
Oh my! It's hard to know where to look!
Konoha, have you found the amulet?
ここでアイテムゲット
Oh my! It's hard to know where to look!
I wonder if this is the amulet.

I think it was just a coincidence, but I was
ambushed by a bandit while checking the amulet.
Well, I took care of them though.
I'm glad you're safe... Thank you so much.

By the way, where is your sister? I can't seem to
find her anywhere.

Today is school. I am studying magic at the Magic
Academy.

Oh, your sister is so diligent in her studies.
Well then, if anything happens again, please let
me know.
ここでアイテムゲット
Oh my! It's hard to know where to look!
Hey Konoha, thanks for the other day.
ここでアイテムゲット
Oh my! It's hard to know where to look!

Ahh! Konoha-san, actually, my sister... my sister
Rudia! She's become a bandit!

It seems like they took me to the cave of the
barrier... I don't know what to do...!

Pull yourself together! You're my sibling, right?
The cave of the barrier... Is it related to the
bandits from the other day, I wonder.

Of course. But if you're coming to the cave, at
least show me something good.

I'm sorry, I'm a little busy right now, so let's
talk later.
